data.description: ***$5000 Buyer Incentive with acceptable offer.*** Spacious Tudor-Cottage style home on greenbelt in highly sought-after Ridge Creek. Boxed ceilings, crown molding, custom cabinets are a few highlights of this well designed home. The downstairs 5th BR w/ built-ins & closet currently used as home office is flex space with plenty of possibilities. Full bath around the corner. Entertain guests in the formal dining with pass through auxiliary kitchen to the main Chef's kitchen featuring farmhouse sink, gas cook top, pot filler, granite counters & large island that opens to spacious living area w/focal point fireplace & TV that disappears behind custom barn doors. Secluded owner retreat down w/spa & roomy walk in closet. Great game room up with built ins & mini fridge for entertaining & easy snack/beverage access. Private secondary bedroom with ensuite bath at top of stairs left. Two additional BRs with magnetic wall b/w for all those important communications & reminders. Covered back porch overlooks greenbelt. Wrought iron & privacy fencing make the yard private & great for entertaining. Tankless water heater. Close to services, shopping, restaurants & road trips up I-10.
